{"word":"G2125 - εὐλαβέομαι - eulabéomai - yoo-lab-eh'-om-ahee - Fear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐλαβέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eulabéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-lab-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to act cautiously, circumspectly"},{"paragraph":"2. to beware, fear"},{"paragraph":"3. to reverence"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G2126 - εὐλαβής - eulabḗs - yoo-lab-ace'/2126\">G2126</a>; to <i>be circumspect</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>be apprehensive</i>; religiously, to <i>reverence:</i> - (moved with) fear.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2125/2125\">G2125</a>, <a href=\"#/G2126/2126\">G2126</a>"}]}